  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to WebKitGTK+</title>

    <para>
      The <application>WebKitGTK+</application> is the port of the portable
      web rendering engine <application>WebKit</application> to the
      <application>GTK+ 2</application> platform.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

